Firm Overview
PICTET NORTH AMERICA ADVISORS SA is an SEC Registered Investment Adviser (RIA). The firm is based in GENEVA 73  SWITZERLAND. As of the firm's last SEC filing on March 31, 2017, the firm has 19 employees and has $2.59 Billion in Regulatory Assets Under Management (RAUM).






