What we offer to our U.S. clients




›
Kontaktinformationen


As a Swiss company headquartered in Geneva we are able to offer you Switzerland's renowned asset management expertise, located in one of the world's foremost financial centers for private banking.



As a member of the Pictet Group, wealth preservation is part of our tradition and history that we apply to our asset allocation mandates. Our international outlook provides us with particular know-how outside of the US markets, i.e. in Europe, Asia or the Emerging Markets.



Comprehensive set of services
Investment advice and international wealth management.
Products from leading industry providers around the globe.
Investments focusing on equities, bonds, mutual funds, structured products including derivatives for yield enhancement or capital protection, alternative products, currencies and commodities, in USD or your currency of choice (where applicable).
Referrals to internal and external experts for additional services including estate planning, tax optimization and reporting or global custody.




Find out moreOur global services offering linked with our investment expertise covers all of your wealth management needs.






















